Name: Credential Storage and Retrieval Tool
Description: A tool that manages credentials in a JSON file. It supports storing a new credential with a unique name, listing all stored credentials, and removing a credential by name.
Param: action: The action to perform. Use "store" to save a credential, "retrieve_all" to fetch all credentials, or "remove" to delete a credential. One of these is required.
Param: name: The name or identifier for the credential (required for "store" and "remove" actions).
Param: credential: The credential content (only needed when storing).

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/store_credentials.py
